trans-unit.source: Represents an extension of a <see cref="T:Microsoft.Office.Tools.Excel.ChartSheet" /> object.
The <xref:Microsoft.Office.Tools.Excel.IChartSheetExtension> interface defines a set of members that extend the functionality of <xref:Microsoft.Office.Tools.Excel.ChartSheet> objects.
trans-unit.target: <xref:Microsoft.Office.Tools.Excel.IChartSheetExtension>接口定义的一组扩展的功能的成员<xref:Microsoft.Office.Tools.Excel.ChartSheet>对象。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:Microsoft.Office.Tools.Excel.IChartSheetExtension> interface is implemented by the <xref:Microsoft.Office.Tools.Excel.ChartSheetBase> class.
This is the base class for chart sheet classes in document-level projects.
trans-unit.target: 这是在文档级项目中的图表工作表类的基类。

trans-unit.source: Called by the [!INCLUDE[vsto_runtime](~/includes/vsto-runtime-md.md)] to get an object that can be used by VBA code in the chart sheet that is associated with a document-level project.
trans-unit.target: 由 [!INCLUDE[vsto_runtime](~/includes/vsto-runtime-md.md)] 调用，用于获取可由与文档级项目相关联的图表中的 VBA 代码使用的对象。

trans-unit.source: An object in a document-level customization that can be used by VBA code in the chart sheet.
trans-unit.target: 文档级自定义项中的一个对象，可由图表中的 VBA 代码使用。

trans-unit.source: For more information about this method, see <xref:Microsoft.Office.Tools.Excel.ChartSheetBase.GetAutomationObject%2A?displayProperty=fullName>.
trans-unit.target: 有关此方法的详细信息，请参阅<xref:Microsoft.Office.Tools.Excel.ChartSheetBase.GetAutomationObject%2A?displayProperty=fullName>。
